Only four fingers left.

01:14:39.972 --> 01:14:42.406
Do you know who I am, Detective?

01:14:43.474 --> 01:14:47.501
Oh, let me guess.

01:14:47.578 --> 01:14:49.569
You're the Engineer.

01:14:52.417 --> 01:14:54.350
I got your message,

01:14:54.418 --> 01:14:56.852
